name: puffypanda #38
description:
This is a story where humans do not exist in this world. All land, seas and air on planet Earth are inhabited by animals of various races. Each race occupies one island on planet Earth.
The Puffy Panda race lives on an island known as Puffy Panda Island. On this island they live like humans. They have jobs, hobbies, paranoia, zodiac signs, and even their own big day celebrations. You must not believe it, right? Follow and observe them, because they will really intrigue you
